### Resolution Step

Recommended updating the Mac's [/etc/hosts](file:///etc/hosts) to:

```bash
100.88.65.71 mydomain.com
```

## Verification Results

### Network Reachability

I verified that the machine remains reachable over Tailscale and that the local services are listening on the expected ports.

